title: Picasso Cafe on Paseo
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Pizza, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Menu details what is veg/vegan and will cater to vegan requests. Vegan choices include a soup, fried portobello with gravy, veggie burger, pizza, eggplant lasagna, desserts. Will cater a 4-course vegan meal to group events with advanced reservation. Brunch on Sundays. Bistro atmosphere with live music on weekends. Local artists artwork hangs on the walls.
